        <strong class="text-highlight">Pitchfork is a well designed website</strong> and I am frequent visitor. One of
        the features I use a lot is this damn carousel.
        I've been using it for years now. I Feel like Bill Murray in Groundhog Day with this thing. Get my morning
        coffee, eat a banana, go to Pitchfork,
        cycle through the albums, repeat. Don't get me wrong, it's a nice carousel but it just hasn't changed in
        forever, so I decided it's time
        for me to take a crack at reinventing it.
    </p>

